<br>
What I would like to see (though not actually AA abilities) are more spells like ION, that work on more types of creatures. One for evil 'lesser races' like dark elves, ogres, and trolls. One for reptiles like iksar and dragons, and perhaps a line for giants. Or instead they could be grouped by the evil diety that created them, like a anti-Veeshan spell that procs on dragons. They wouldn't stack with each other so a smart paladin will have to come to a fight prepared.<br>
<br>
As for Shields, I've always liked the improved parry, or adding a shield based block (perhaps linked to the bash skill). But as an alternative, perhaps giving shield bashes a chance to proc (with spell-based procs) and adding shields that have innate procs like  weapons.<br>
