<br>
Level: 60<br>
Class: Paladin<br>
Cost: 600<br>
Effect: Summon a level 30 Paladin Pet with the capability to add armor and weapons. Also casts, but only on it's self (Center/Holy Armor/Symbol) LoH's on it's self as well.<br>
<br>
Sweet but nothing compared to the melee of an SK pet at the same level. It of course could not tank so it wouldn't be over powering, and of course, it would be great RPing.<br>
<br>
Restrictions: Pally type mob so no duel weilding, no kicking and no bashing unless he has shield, then he'll bash like the usual necro pet. Pet would look like the casters race, per example, Human casts it, human squire. If a erudite casts it though, Erudite squire, just like Beastlords pets. Max hit could be a tad bit lower than usualy hit as a 30 paladin. Able to wear armor and able to riposte, double attack and has 1/2 the mana pool of average 30 paladin to make the casting balanced.<br>
